reviewText: I found this to be rather disappointing. Jessica is a beautiful girl, but the video of her talking was obviously dubbed over and the video segments, particularly at the end, were so short, you didn't get to see very much. It would have been better if there were some alternate endings to make things less predictable and give it more replay value. I thought this had a great deal of unrealized potential and was an OK game but could have been a lot more interesting.Seduction Poker - Volume 1 - Jessica
